data.meta_description: Boleslaw III Wrymouth OF POLAND was born on August 20, 1086 in Poland, son of Wladyslaw I Herman OF POLAND and Judith OF BOHEMIA. He was married in the year 1102 to Zbyslava OF KIEV, they gave birth to 1 child. He was married in the year 1115 to Salomea OF BERG, they had 5 children. He died on October 28, 1138 in Sochaczew, Poland. This information is part of Family tree Riny Doyle geboren Marinus van Waard by Riny Doyle on Genealogy Online.
